">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3o-ph%C3%A1t/poem-QTVFJ9Z0-BPrKIIARvfJrA">Tảo phát - 早發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thanh-Kh%C3%A2u-t%E1%BB%AD-ca/poem-1cDYBHKHiWXC3r_OhZMuig">Thanh Khâu tử ca - 青丘子歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Th%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Ho%C3%A0ng-kh%E1%BA%A3o-ki%E1%BA%BFn-th%E1%BA%BF-nghi%E1%BB%87p/poem-7Mr-V79IWSb5ON5eGonAPQ">Thất đề - Hoàng khảo kiến thế nghiệp - 失題－皇考建世業</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-s%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0/poem-yezq_vKXfawT8Q8cIlAS9A">Ức tích sơn cư - 憶昔山居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-CF4h4cy0l6rugNx2hdZfpQ">Chiêm Đồng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
